hen there is obvious intent to abuse and/or misuse restricted round-trip fa=
res.</span></li><li>The purchase and use of round-trip Tickets for the purp=
ose of one-way travel only, known as "Throwaway Ticketing," is prohibited b=
y Alaska.</li><li>Fares apply for travel only between the points for which =
