ou paid. If you paid for a first-class seat and were downgraded and elect t=
o travel, we will refund you the difference between the fare you paid and t=
he applicable Main Cabin fare if there is a fare difference.</span></li><li=
><span class=3D"decimal">Delayed Checked Baggage. If Alaska collected bagga=
